      "rationale": "The validation activities directly replicate the COU: the same non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw geometry, the same ASTM F1717 compression-bending loading protocol, and the same fixture boundary conditions used in the regulatory submission. The FEA model ensemble spans three independent modeling teams (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes), providing additional confidence in model-form independence. The validation scenario is therefore assessed as highly relevant to the COU."
