    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All three QoIs satisfy the pre-established acceptance bounds (E/uval < 1.96; percent difference < 10%). Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single shortfall (Test conditions, achieved level 2 vs. required level 3) is accepted given the regulatory standard status of ASTM F1717 and the consistency of results across two independent laboratories. The overall credibility evidence is judged sufficient to support the regulatory submission claim for the non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct.",
